# The image builds node_modules in its own `deps` stage (npm install from
# package-lock.json), then `COPY . .`. Without excluding the host node_modules,
# that COPY drags local pnpm symlinks (e.g. @base-ui/react -> ../.pnpm/...) on
# top of the deps-stage real directories, failing with
# "cannot replace to directory ... with file". Exclude build artifacts from the
# context entirely; the image is self-contained.
node_modules
dist
.git
*.log
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
